creator: Lamington Games Pty Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Start playing Words Collide today - a beautiful cooperative word game about building word combos together.

Match and discover words to achieve new high scores! Carefully construct combos to maximise your score and set your friends up for success.

Arrange letters to spell words; your friends can reuse your words to spell bigger words.

Earn coins to unlock upgrades like extra letters, hints and deep cascade combos.

Download Words Collide, and cooperate together with friends!
descriptionShort: The cutest cooperative word game! Spell words and play with friends today!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Matchmaking Multiplayer Update!

Added the much requested feature to play cooperative mode with other plays.
Added a 'Play Again' button on the end screen.
Polished the shop screen UI.
(956) Fixed bug where losing and regaining app focus would trigger previously opened notification links.
(978) Fixed bug where opening notifications while game is closed could cause you to lose store upgrade and coin progress.
(978) Fixed bug where AdScreen would display under the 'Play Turn' button.

title: Words Collide

creator: Lamington Games Pty Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Words Collide is a refreshingly clever word game.
- Play by yourself or cooperatively with friends.
- Relax in Zen Mode, or challenge yourself with Advanced Mode.

- Discover and learn new words using our in game dictionary.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
This update adds lots of requested improvements

Toggle Sound and Haptic Feedback
Now on the Pause screen you can toggle Music, SFX, or Haptic Feedback features.

Hints Rework
Wordy's hints have been merged with the hint button, so players will always see a basic hint before committing to using a full hint.

Bug fixes!
Fixed several bugs caused from using the rematch feature in multiplayer mode.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Sound & Multiplayer Update

-Multiplayer games will now expire if the active player doesn’t play their turn fast enough.
-Matchmade turns will last 3 days, turns with friends will last 8 days.
-Lots of new Sound Effects!.
-Pressing the Singleplayer menu button will transition you straight to Singleplayer Zen mode if you haven’t unlocked Advanced mode.
-The hint tutorial has been reworked again, sorry to anyone who got annoyed by the previous version!
- Plenty More Bug fixes!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Update 0.9.4 Patch Notes:

Score Rebalancing & Highlight Sharing

Important changes:
The scoring formula for words and cascades have been changed to stop being exponential after different points.
There are new leaderboards for each mode, the old leaderboards will be viewable but you won't be able to submit to them anymore.
Your current Cooperative HighScores have been reset to 0. We have saved what they were, so we can display them later in a stats screen.
